    public class ToggleDefineProtocol
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.Button
implements com.google.gwt.event.dom.client.ClickHandler
    ToggleButton that can be used to indicate if a protocol is being defined. If not in default state, then adding a step will execute it immediately.
    Author:
    Group Fingerpaint
